Ya, kau memerankan Joan.

778
00:49:16,000 --> 00:49:17,000
Siapa itu Joan Sumber?

779
00:49:17,080 --> 00:49:18,360
Joan yang asli.

780
00:49:18,440 --> 00:49:20,760
Lihat itu. Joan Sumber.

781
00:49:21,600 --> 00:49:22,600
Joan Sumber?

782
00:49:24,760 --> 00:49:26,040
Aku bukan Joan asli?

783
00:49:26,120 --> 00:49:28,080
Kau salah satu versi Joan

784
